name: My name is the one who breaks the shackles
description: Remember the image, rotate the whirlpool, the color of the rune depends on what level it affects, your consciousness should color the rune itself. It can be presented everywhere and nowhere, most effectively inside the body, your consciousness itself should tell you where... Its application is getting rid of everything that bothers you. She will help to let go of the old and switch to a new reality. Its power is in removing and weakening obsessive thoughts and emotions. The indicator that you have applied it correctly is immediate relaxation.
